01:59.320 --> 02:00.880
Oke, Xiong Yuanbao.

02:01.040 --> 02:02.080
Kamu hebat juga, ya.

02:02.080 --> 02:04.340
Sebaiknya kamu ingat ucapanmu barusan.

02:04.360 --> 02:06.320
